TextEng: Except for your clothes, you look like Aribeth de Tylmarande!
Text: 옷만 빼면 아리베스 드 틸마란데처럼 생겼는데요!

TextEng: You look like Aribeth! 'Cept you dress different.
She was a hero of our people, once. Until she fell and betrayed us to Morag.
Text: 한때는 우리 백성의 영웅이었죠. 타락해서 우리를 모라그에게 넘기기 전까지는요.

TextEng: She is a foul traitor in the service of Morag!
Aribeth used be nice lady. Then she become bad and serve Morag.
Text: 아리베스 원래 좋은 사람이었어. 근데 나빠지고 모라그 섬기게 됐어.

TextEng: Aribeth be traitor who serve Morag!
You speak of many places I have never heard of.
How did you get here?
Why do you want to kill Morag?
I've heard this tale before. I'll just kill you before you betray me.
Text: 이 이야기는 전에도 들었어요. 날 배신하기 전에 죽이겠어요.

TextEng: Goodbye.
You say strange place names. Me not know them.
Text: 이상한 장소 이름 말해. 나 모르는 곳이야.

TextEng: How you get here?
Why you want kill Morag?
Me hear this before. Me kill you before you turn on me like Aribeth done.
Text: 나 이거 전에 들었어. 아리베스처럼 배신하기 전에 죽여야겠어.

TextEng: You remind me of Aribeth.
You remind me of Aribeth.
What do you mean?
Aribeth betrayed me - I can't take the same chance with you. You must die!
Text: 아리베스가 날 배신했어요. 당신한테도 똑같이 당할 순 없어요. 죽어야겠어요!

TextEng: What you mean?
Aribeth be bad traitor. Me not take chance with you. You die now!
Text: 아리베스 나쁜 배신자야. 나 너한테도 똑같이 안 당해. 지금 죽어!

TextEng: Save it. I don't trust you and you must die!
Save it. Me not trust you. You die now!
Text: 그만해. 나 안 믿어. 지금 죽어!

TextEng: Failed? How have you failed?
What you mean? How you fail?
And you have come seeking vengeance.
And you want kill them for get even.
What is it that you must tell me?
What you got tell me that be so important?
Me not listen to you no more!
Forget it. I'm not listening to you!
What this magic thingy do?
Text: 이 마법 물건 뭐 하는 거야?

TextEng: Okay, me take magic thingy from you and go kill Morag.
Text: 좋아, 나 마법 물건 가져가서 모라그 죽이러 갈게.

TextEng: What does this artifact do?
Give me the artifact. I'll use it to help defeat Morag.
Text: 유물을 주세요. 모라그를 물리치는 데 쓸게요.
